45:07.320 --> 45:10.529
He'd found a protagonist
for his book.

45:10.640 --> 45:13.246
Little Matt.

45:13.360 --> 45:16.091
- Chapter one.
- I look like shit.

45:16.200 --> 45:18.089
- Rough day?
- Rough life, Jack.

45:18.200 --> 45:20.009
