45:29.840 --> 45:32.002
- I'll tell
you later.

45:34.600 --> 45:36.409
- Change.

45:36.520 --> 45:39.205
$5,000.

45:39.320 --> 45:42.529
- What has happened to Bella?
- What's happened to Bella?

45:42.640 --> 45:43.926
- She's been re-assigned.

45:44.040 --> 45:47.362
- Not re-assigned,
just written out of the story.

45:47.480 --> 45:49.960
- Good evening.

45:50.080 --> 45:51.844
- Hundreds.

45:51.960 --> 45:54.850
- Change. 1,000.

45:56.800 --> 45:59.041
