46:35.840 --> 46:37.842
Eleven double.

46:37.960 --> 46:39.007
Twenty one.

46:39.120 --> 46:42.806
18,17,17...

46:42.920 --> 46:46.891
13, 20.

46:53.840 --> 46:54.648
Change.

46:54.760 --> 46:55.727
He knew
how to fix it for her.

46:55.840 --> 46:57.524
$1,000.

46:57.640 --> 46:59.768
His father
had taught him the trick.

47:04.360 --> 47:05.521
