47:48.760 --> 47:51.843
He ought to thank her.

47:51.960 --> 47:53.485
- Pretty woman.

47:53.640 --> 47:55.881
- Jani De Villiers
had just entered his book.

47:56.000 --> 47:58.401
Place your bets, please.

48:10.520 --> 48:13.330
- Yeah.
- How's it going, Jacko?

48:13.440 --> 48:16.250
- Fine. I took that job.
- Good for you.

48:16.360 --> 48:17.407
- I was wondering
what was happening.

48:17.520 --> 48:18.487
- Yeah, well, I
tried to call you,

48:18.600 --> 48:20.523
but they said your
line was disconnected.

48:20.640 --> 48:22.290
- Ah, yes.

48:22.400 --> 48:25.563
I moved house.
I needed a bigger place.

48:25.680 --> 48:27.205
- How's that book
of yours coming on?

48:27.320 --> 48:30.085
- Yeah. I'm
getting there.

48:30.200 --> 48:31.122
- Well, it's a good job
you've got the job

48:31.240 --> 48:33.208
to fall back on,
isn't it? Huh?

