Oh, there's my
other line. Ciao.

48:51.720 --> 48:53.688
- I don't like it.

48:56.960 --> 48:58.928
- Why not?

48:59.080 --> 49:02.209
- I don't like it at all.

49:02.320 --> 49:05.290
