hope in it.

49:56.000 --> 49:58.526
- It's the truth.

49:58.680 --> 50:00.887
- Without hope, there's
no point to anything.

50:01.000 --> 50:04.129
- What is so fucking
hopeful about your job?

50:04.240 --> 50:06.925
Spending the day catching
poor people stealing?

50:07.040 --> 50:09.281
You said yourself the organized
gangs get away with it.

50:09.440 --> 50:11.249
At least in the casino
everyone gets caught.

50:11.400 --> 50:14.370
Rich or poor, the odds are
the same, it's all relative.

50:14.480 --> 50:18.280
- Crap! It is not
relative. It's unfair.

50:18.400 --> 50:21.370
- It's designed unfair,
like your casino, and your

50:21.480 --> 50:24.165
croupier's a little shit,
because he goes along with it.

50:24.280 --> 50:26.886
- Yeah? What
about the lottery?

50:27.040 --> 50:28.883
Look at this, you're just like

50:29.000 --> 50:30.445
all the other
suckers out there.

50:30.560 --> 50:33.484
14 and a half million to one,
is that your idea of hope?

50:33.600 --> 50:34.965
- The door, Jack.
- Leave it.

50:35.080 --> 50:37.481
- No. Answer it.

50:47.440 --> 50:50.125
- Just called round to say
thanks for shopping me, Jack.

50:52.120 --> 50:54.487
- What are you
talking about?

50:54.600 --> 50:57.171
- Reynolds got a doctor in. They
forced me to do a dope test

50:57.320 --> 50:59.448
which was positive,
as you knew.

50:59.560 --> 51:01.324
- I don't know
anything about it.

51:02.520 --> 51:04.443
- Hiya.
- Hi.

51:04.560 --> 51:06.289
- Your boyfriend fucked me,
smoked my dope,

51:06.400 --> 51:09.449
