- All men are scumbags.
- I agree.

51:29.000 --> 51:31.844
Go on.
Go after her.

51:35.600 --> 51:39.650
- He was Jack...
and he was Jake.

51:39.760 --> 51:41.410
And he had discovered
there was a price to pay

51:41.520 --> 51:43.887
