was staying, or with whom.

51:50.720 --> 51:53.929
He realized he knew little
about her life, but then...

51:54.040 --> 51:56.042
He had never
asked about it.

52:06.720 --> 52:08.085
For the first time
in a long while,

52:08.200 --> 52:10.202
