or the betrayed.

52:38.400 --> 52:39.811
- Thanks for the
information.

52:39.920 --> 52:41.968
- Pleasure.

52:42.080 --> 52:44.287
Pity about Bella.

52:44.400 --> 52:47.244
- She was a real asset.

52:47.360 --> 52:49.362
What could I do?

52:51.800 --> 52:54.883
Sorry, Jack.
No smoking in the nest.

53:02.080 --> 53:04.208
- Thank you, sir.

53:04.320 --> 53:07.164
- Fantastic, brilliant.
- Just down the side.

53:08.480 --> 53:11.051
Jack?

53:11.160 --> 53:13.288
I thought it was you,
It's the hair.

53:13.400 --> 53:15.243
- Listen, I'm working
on that soccer story.

53:15.360 --> 53:17.886
- Right. Look, I must
get back to Habib.

53:18.000 --> 53:20.924
