- Thanks.

54:02.000 --> 54:03.764
Books piled like chips.

54:03.880 --> 54:06.929
Stack 'em high, sell 'em
fast, make a killing.

54:07.040 --> 54:09.168
No dumb soccer
novel for Jack.

54:09.280 --> 54:11.567
