the world he knew.

54:11.680 --> 54:13.762
From the inside.

54:15.760 --> 54:17.728
Chapter four.

54:26.520 --> 54:29.205
I don't know how you can
drive at night in those glasses.

54:33.200 --> 54:35.009
How'd you hurt
your hand?

54:35.120 --> 54:37.930
- Oh, it was just an accident.
- It's nothing.

54:39.160 --> 54:41.606
- Should be the
next on the right.

54:44.240 --> 54:47.244
