us to share a room.

54:53.560 --> 54:55.767
- That's fine.

55:09.960 --> 55:13.407
Look.

55:13.520 --> 55:16.364
It's no use pretending
it was an accident.

55:16.480 --> 55:19.643
I had a fight with someone.
