55:31.960 --> 55:34.566
- She's a dab hand with
the racket, your friend.

55:35.840 --> 55:37.649
- South African women
are very sporty.

55:37.760 --> 55:39.922
- So I see.

55:44.680 --> 55:46.170
- Nice serve.

55:46.320 --> 55:48.561
- 14-15.

55:48.680 --> 55:52.002
- How did she
get that shiner?

55:52.160 --> 55:54.925
- I found her in
bed with someone.

55:55.080 --> 55:57.924
- Who was he?
- She.

56:00.040 --> 56:01.724
- I say, you're a
dark horse, Jack.

56:01.840 --> 56:04.446
- Lovely shot.
- Nice game.

56:07.520 --> 56:10.126
- Come on, Jack.
- I don't gamble.

56:10.240 --> 56:12.561
- Don't be a spoil-sport.
- It's only a few quid.

56:12.720 --> 56:14.961
- It's nothing to do with
