56:41.000 --> 56:44.322
- I'll deal, but
I won't play.

56:44.440 --> 56:46.681
- Sure you know how?

56:49.960 --> 56:52.930
The hands of a conjurer.

56:54.840 --> 56:58.686
Or a cardsharp.

57:17.240 --> 57:21.040
- Okay, last hand.
- I've got an idea.

57:21.160 --> 57:23.049
- No. No stripping.

57:23.160 --> 57:26.881
- Right, we're not having
that again. Although...

57:28.480 --> 57:30.448
- I'll stick to bluffing.

57:30.560 --> 57:32.722
