58:55.120 --> 58:56.610
- Oh Shit.

58:56.760 --> 59:01.209
- Not so fast, darling.
- A full house.

59:01.320 --> 59:03.971
- Hang on, chaps,
that's impossible.

59:04.960 --> 59:07.691
- Well how's about
this for impossible?

59:07.800 --> 59:09.450
Four of a kind.

59:09.560 --> 59:10.800
What's going on?

59:10.920 --> 59:14.242
- No.

59:14.400 --> 59:16.402
- Straight flush.

59:16.520 --> 59:17.931
- What are the odds
of this happening?

59:18.040 --> 59:21.806
- Thousands to one.
- 42,300,000 to one.

59:21.920 --> 59:23.365
- Approximately.

59:23.480 --> 59:25.847
- Could have won if
I'd been able to bluff.

59:27.400 --> 59:30.210
- I get it.

59:30.320 --> 59:32.482
- Get what?

59:33.720 --> 59:35.643
